{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/extras/about33.png?t=1737399406\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Theralite is a traditional turn based Roguelike.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a distant planet, in the deep crystal mines, players try to survive and find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mine for gems, explore, trade, battle monsters in the deep and survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is a traditional turn based game, but the steps are animated.\u00a0The world moves and reacts only when player does. That means you can take your time and plan ahead...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some level tiles can be mined by player and yield different forms of loot and treasure. Beware, however, as the mining activity can also make (more) nasties aware of your presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Player has to scavenge for survival and figure out how to escape the deep crystal caverns and mining facilities after a disastrous event.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/extras/pickaxe2.png?t=1737399406\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737399406","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/page.bg.jpg?t=1737399406","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/3972584b011a5457897775cd7b0c66239e1ca1d9/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737399406","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445690/3972584b011a5457897775cd7b0c66239e1ca1d9/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737399406","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids